{"id":130112,"type":2,"name":"The New Fantastic Four","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/6c/3c/130112_Xg5XZ.jpg","summary":"　　It is the second animated series based on Marvel's comic book series Fantastic Four. The 1978 series replaced the character of the Human Torch with a robot named H.E.R.B.I.E., (Humanoid Experimental Robot, B-type, Integrated Electronics). A long-lasting rumor stated that this change was made by the TV network (NBC) because executives did not want young viewers to imitate the Human Torch by setting themselves on fire. This rumor proved to be untrue, as the 1978 television rights to use that character were tied up by a proposed television pilot movie in development by Universal Studios that ended up never being produced.","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>13</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1978-09-09</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/6769\">Marvel Entertainment, LLC</a></li><li><span>播放电视台: </span>NBC</li><li><span>播放结束: </span>1978-12-16</li><li><span>IMDb: </span>tt0241100</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"霹雳火机器人","count":1},{"name":"Marvel","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":511909,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/511909","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":511910,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/511910","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":511911,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/511911","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":511912,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/511912","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":511913,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/511913","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":511914,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/511914","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","aird